      • addAppointment

        public static java.lang.String addAppointment​(java.lang.String title,
                                              java.lang.String description,
                                              java.lang.String location,
                                              java.lang.String type,
                                              java.sql.Timestamp startTime,
                                              java.sql.Timestamp endTime,
                                              java.lang.String createdBy,
                                              java.lang.String lastUpdatedBy,
                                              java.lang.Integer customerID,
                                              java.lang.Integer user_ID,
                                              java.lang.Integer contactID)
        Method adds an appointment to the appointment table with the parameters provided.
        Parameters:
        title - Title provided by the user to be added to the appointment table.
        description - Description provided by the user to be added to the appointment table.
        location - Location provided by the user to be added to the appointment table.
        type - Type provided by the user to be added to the appointment table.
        startTime - Start time provided by the user and converted to UTC time then added to the appointment table.
        endTime - End time provided by the startTime and 1 added hour to the appointment. Appointment is then added to the appointment table.
        createdBy - Created time provided by the login function when the user logs in. To be added to the appointment table.
        lastUpdatedBy - Last Updated By name provided by the login function. Gets added to the appointment table.
        customerID - Customer ID selected by the user and added to the appointment table.
        user_ID - User ID provided by the user once logged in.
        contactID - Contacted ID provided by the user when selecting a contact in the drop down list.
        Returns:
        Returns an appointment object so it can be added into the appointment table.

      • updateAppointment

        public static void updateAppointment​(java.lang.String title,
                                     java.lang.String description,
                                     java.lang.String location,
                                     java.lang.String type,
                                     java.sql.Timestamp start,
                                     java.sql.Timestamp end,
                                     java.lang.String lastUpdatedBy,
                                     java.lang.Integer customerID,
                                     java.lang.Integer userID,
                                     java.lang.Integer contactID,
                                     java.lang.Integer appointmentID)
        Method takes data from the update appointment screen.
        Parameters:
        title - Updated Title provided by the user to update the title field in the appointment table.
        description - Description provided by the user to update the description field in the appointment table.
        location - Location provided by the user to update the location field in the appointment table.
        type - Type provided by the user to update the type field in the appointment table.
        start - Start provided from StartTime Local Date Time field.
        end - End provided from the End Time Local Date Time Field.
        lastUpdatedBy - Last updated by provided by the login field once the user logs in.
        customerID - Customer ID provided from the customer combo box.
        userID - User ID that is provided by the login screen once the user logs in.
        contactID - Provided by the contact combo box from the user's selection.
        appointmentID - Appointment ID that is not editable by the user.
